i-MSCP Roundcube Webmail suite composer package

Version 1.0.0
    Added: Cron task for cleanup of database
    Added: LOGROTATE(8) configuration file for rotation of log files
    Enhancement: Make use of APC cache for IMAP indexes cache
    Removed: ROUNDCUBE_VERSION parameter in roundcube.data file
    Review: IMAP authentication type now set explicitly to 'PLAIN'
    Review: Log IMAP session identifiers after each IMAP login
    Review: Log successful/failed logins to <log_dir>/userlogins
    Review: Log session authentication errors to <log_dir>/session
    Review: Make use of the built-in spell checker
    Review: SMTP authentication type now set explicitly to 'PLAIN'
    Review: Nginx configuration file
    Security: Make use of better cipher for encryption (AES-256-CBC instead of default DES-EDE3-CBC)
